---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import LiquidGlassNav from "../components/LiquidGlassNav.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Experience - Piyush Jain"
  description="Work experience and mentorship"
>
  <LiquidGlassNav />
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Experience</h1>

    <!-- Work Experience Section -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Work Experience</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <article class="border-l-4 border-border dark:border-border pl-6">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between mb-2"
          >
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">
                Technology Consultant - Automation & DevSecOps
              </h3>
              <p class="text-muted">
                Hewlett Packard Enterprise (via Mphasis Ltd.) • Pune, India
              </p>
            </div>
            <time class="text-sm text-muted mt-1 sm:mt-0"
              >Aug 2025 – Present</time
            >
          </div>
          <ul
            class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-muted mt-4"
          >
            <li>
              Developed multithreaded Python module for server firmware upgrades
              across <span class="font-semibold text-text"
                >100+ servers</span
              >, including local HTTP service hosting multi-GB ISO images with
              comprehensive logging and robust error handling.
            </li>
            <li>
              Reduced manual effort by over <span
                class="font-semibold text-text">95%</span
              > by automating slow, error-prone upgrade processes complicated by undocumented
              hardware behavior.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Python</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >HTTP</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Automation</span
            >
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="border-l-4 border-border dark:border-border pl-6">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between mb-2"
          >
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Technology Consultant Intern</h3>
              <p class="text-muted">
                Hewlett Packard Enterprise (via Mphasis Ltd.) • Pune, India
              </p>
            </div>
            <time class="text-sm text-muted mt-1 sm:mt-0"
              >Feb 2025 – Aug 2025</time
            >
          </div>
          <ul
            class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-muted mt-4"
          >
            <li>
              Automated log rotation and server-profile backups using Python,
              Ansible, AWX, and GitLab, improving reliability across managed
              Linux systems.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Python</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Ansible</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >AWX</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >GitLab</span
            >
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="border-l-4 border-border dark:border-border pl-6">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between mb-2"
          >
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">
                Data Science & Machine Learning Intern
              </h3>
              <p class="text-muted">
                MITU Skillologies • Pune, India
              </p>
            </div>
            <time class="text-sm text-muted mt-1 sm:mt-0"
              >Feb 2024 – Mar 2024</time
            >
          </div>
          <ul
            class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-muted mt-4"
          >
            <li>
              Built supervised learning model to classify chord harmonies in
              Bach chorales using feature-engineered musical attributes.
            </li>
            <li>
              Optimized Random Forest and SVM via grid search, achieving <span
                class="font-semibold text-text"
                >78.95%</span
              > accuracy.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Python</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >scikit-learn</span
            >
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mentorship Section -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Mentorship & Teaching</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <article
          class="p-6 border border-[rgb(var(--border-color))] rounded-lg"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">
            Game Dev Utopia (GDU) — Technical Workshop Lead & Design Team Member
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2">
            PICT • 2022 – 2025
          </p>
          <ul
            class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-muted"
          >
            <li>
              Designed and led technical workshops on Blender 3D covering
              modeling, materials, lighting, and rendering from first
              principles.
            </li>
            <li>
              Mentored participants to complete independent 3D projects; all
              attendees produced renders demonstrating applied skills.
            </li>
            <li>
              Served on design team for inter-college events; created primary
              promotional poster for Paricharcha x Glitched.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills Section -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Skills</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 border border-[rgb(var(--border-color))] rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Technical</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Python</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >JavaScript</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >TypeScript</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >React</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-[rgb(var(--border-color))] rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Tools & Platforms</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Git</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >Docker</span
            >
            <span
              class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-surface dark:bg-surface rounded-full"
              >AWS</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
